---
title: One-Pan Chicken and Couscous Pilaf with Peas, Almonds, and Spicy Crema
description: You could describe this dish as “feast of the Middle East,” since it has chicken and couscous studded with an array of veggies and Turkish-style spices. But we have a couple other words for it: “dead simple.” That’s because it uses only one pan and can be on the table in as little as 20 minutes. All you’ve got to do is a little bit of chopping and stovetop cooking while the couscous steams and voila! It’s ready.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pan-chicken-and-couscous-pilaf-7e7cbd78.jpg
